This file tracks the status of releases in the 1.4.x line.

See "Stabilizing and maintaining releases" in trunk/www/hacking.html for
details on how release lines and voting work, what kinds of bugs can
delay a release, etc.

Status of 1.4.0:
================

Candidate changes:

  * r21204, r21205, r21212, r21213, r21218
    Makes the po-status tools run with less tweaking.
    Justification:
      Useful for checking po status on the branch without having to
      manually copy the new versions from trunk. (Please don't block
      an rc on this though!)
    Votes:
      +1: glasser

Approved changes:

  * r21207
    Rename svnadmin create's '--no-svndiff1' to '--pre-1.4-compatible'.
    Justification:
      --no-svndiff1 is poor user interface.
    Votes:
      +1: maxb, danderson, malcolm


